Known bugs for blowssi 0.2.0 --------------------------------------------------

  - DCC chat, /notice and /ctcp are not encrypted.
  - No automatic new query window on new crypt messages:
    When keyx is initiated by someone else, and no query window is open, their
    text will go into the status window until a query window is opened by the 
    user.

Known bugs for blowssi 0.1.0 --------------------------------------------------

  - There have been problems reported with encryption/decryption 
    for scandinavian characters, umlauts, unicode,...

  - DCC chat, /notice and /ctcp are not encrypted.

  - Actions (/me) not encrypted.
